Package org.icepdf.core.pobjects.graphics.RasterOps

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBufferedImageOp
    A convenience class which implements those methods of BufferedImageOp which are rarely changed.
    CMYKRasterOp
    Raster operation for converting a CMYK colour to RGB using an a rough algorithm which generally results in images that are darker then they should be.
    ConvolveFilter
    A filter which applies a convolution kernel to an image.
    DecodeRasterOp
    Applies the decode value array tot he specified raster.
    GaussianFilter
    A filter which applies Gaussian blur to an image.
    GrayRasterOp
    Applies an algorithm to convert the Gray colour space to RGB.
    IccCmykRasterOp
    Raster operation for converting a CMYK colour to RGB using an ICC colour profile.
    ImageMath
    A class containing static math methods useful for image processing.
    PColorSpaceRasterOp
    Convert a rgb encoded raster to the specified colour space.
    PixelUtils
    Some more useful math functions for image processing.
    SmartBlurFilter  
    YCbCrARasterOp
    Raster operation that convers the YCbCrA to a ARGB colour space.
    YCbCrRasterOp
    Raster operation that convers the YCbCr to a RGB colour space.
    YCCKRasterOp
    The basic idea is that we do a fuzzy colour conversion from YCCK to CMYK.
